# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# IMPORTANT: Files to COMMIT (not ignore)
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# The following fluxid QA files MUST be committed:
#   .hooks/                      - Hook scripts (read-only)
#   .pre-commit-config.yaml     - Pre-commit framework config
#   .gitleaks.toml              - Secrets detection config
#   .jscpdrc                    - Code duplication config
#   .semgrep/                   - Security pattern rules
#   backend/pyproject.toml      - Python tool configurations
#   frontend/eslint.config.js   - ESLint configuration
#   frontend/tsconfig.json      - TypeScript configuration
